'The gen'l'm'n can't go in just now , said a shambling pot boy , with a red head , 'cos' Mr. Lowten's a singin' a comic song , and he'll put him out . 
He'll be done directly , Sir . 
The puffy faced young man rose , and drawing a chair close to Mr. Pickwick in an obscure corner of the room , listened attentively to his tale of woe . 
