'Is she ? said Mr. Pickwick . 
'Very , said Mr. Magnus . 
She lives about twenty miles from here , Mr. Pickwick . 
I heard she would be here to night and all to morrow forenoon , and came down to seize the opportunity . 
I think an inn is a good sort of a place to propose to a single woman in , Mr. Pickwick . 
She is more likely to feel the loneliness of her situation in travelling , perhaps , than she would be at home . 
