Had heard Pickwick ask the little boy how he should like to have another father . 
Did not know that Mrs. Bardell was at that time keeping company with the baker , but did know that the baker was then a single man and is now married . 
fainted away stone dead when Mr. Sanders asked her to name the day , and believed that everybody as called herself a lady would do the same , under similar circumstances . 
