'What a lucky feller you are ! 'How do you mean ? inquired the gentleman in blue . 
'That 'ere young lady , replied Sam . 
'She knows wot's wot , she does . 
Mr. Weller closed one eye , and shook his head from side to side , in a manner which was highly gratifying to the personal vanity of the gentleman in blue . 
'I'm afraid your a cunning fellow , Mr. Weller , said that individual . 
'No , no , said Sam . 
'I leave all that 'ere to you . 
