It's a legal fiction , my dear sir , nothing more . 
Saying which , the attorney shrugged his shoulders , smiled , took a second pinch of snuff , and led the way into the office of the judge's clerk . 
Nor were the conversations of these gentlemen the only sounds that broke upon the ear . 
A clerk hurried in with a bundle of papers , and stared about him . 
'Sniggle and Blink , cried the tenor . 
'Porkin and Snob , growled the bass . 
