Or stop I'll tell you what I'll tell you how we'll do him , said Smangle , with a cunning look . 
'How ? said Mr. Pickwick . 
'Send down word that he's to spend the change in cigars . 
Run and tell him that d'ye hear ? They shan't be wasted , continued Smangle , turning to Mr. Pickwick . 
In which , to show his sincerity , he forthwith pledged the company in a draught which half emptied it . 
Nor were the two last named gentlemen as much edified as they might have been by the moving passages narrated . 
'Well will you know me again ? said Mr. Smangle , with a frown . 
'I'd svear to you anyveres , Sir , replied Sam cheerfully . 
