By the time the officer arrived , Sam had made himself so extremely popular , that the congregated gentlemen determined to see him to prison in a body . 
So off they set the plaintiff and defendant walking arm in arm , the officer in front , and eight stout coachmen bringing up the rear . 
At Serjeant's Inn Coffee house the whole party halted to refresh , and , the legal arrangements being completed , the procession moved on again . 
Nothing but these little incidents occurred on the way . 
