'Of course , replied Bob . 
With this explanation of the phenomenon of the shutters , Mr. Bob Sawyer pointed to the shop , and relapsed into an ecstasy of mirth . 
'Bless me , you are surely not mad enough to think of leaving your patients without anybody to attend them ! remonstrated Mr. Pickwick in a very serious tone . 
'Why not ? asked Bob , in reply . 
'I shall save by it , you know . 
None of them ever pay . 
So it's all for the best . 
There was a philosophy and a strength of reasoning about this reply , which Mr. Pickwick was not prepared for . 
He paused a few moments , and added , less firmly than before 'But this chaise , my young friend , will only hold two and I am pledged to Mr. Allen . 
