All this was most embarrassing to Mr. Pickwick , the more especially as Mr. Winkle , senior , evinced palpable astonishment at the eccentric not to say extraordinary behaviour of his two companions . 
You will see , by its contents , that on your favourable and fatherly consideration of it , depend his future happiness and welfare . 
